      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for everything from grocery runs to weekend getaways. It still looks great and drives even better\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable set of wheels without the brand-new price tag. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
