    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The six-speed manual gearbox offers precise engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. This example retains its factory carbon fiber roof for a lower center of gravity and features an updated suspension geometry with refreshed bushings. Meticulously maintained with recent Blackstone oil analysis confirming rod bearing health. A driver-focused machine with excellent mechanical feedback and a visceral induction note from the individual throttle bodies.",
