    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 in Eminent White Pearl offers a perfect balance of luxury and dependability. Having been garage-kept and strictly maintained according to the manufacturer's schedule, this vehicle presents beautifully. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the forward hood consistent with highway commuting. Inside, the Parchment leather interior remains supple and clean; the cabin is a non-smoker environment and free of pet hair. You will find very light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. All electronic features, including the premium audio system and heated/ventilated seats, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound with a complete service history available. It recently underwent a full multi-point inspection, an oil change, and a tire rotation. The Michelin tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide a smooth, confident bite. This is a turn-key luxury SUV ready for its next owner to enjoy miles of quiet, comfortable travel.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
