      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s still in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-cared for, runs super smoothly, and is just waiting for a new owner to get behind the wheel. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways\u2014come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
