    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E92 M3 featuring the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, an engine celebrated for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit delivers power through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis retains its precision with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and hydraulic-assist steering providing unfiltered feedback. Maintenance is up to date, notably including preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are primed for high-load cycles. It sits on staggered alloy wheels wrapped in high-performance rubber, maintaining the ideal 50/50 weight distribution this platform is known for.",
